      <guid>http://example.com/2022/02/09/%E8%BF%BD%E6%83%B3%E8%BD%AE%E5%9B%9E/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Feb 2022 06:19:51 GMT</pubDate>
      
      <description>&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;遇见你真是太好了
